// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0256 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 620d208b-9292-5519-b96d-66b53c831023

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*photon os:3.0*")
